Uses of Class
fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.processors.EmotionMLProcessor

Packages that use EmotionMLProcessor
fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.processors Contains all processors, exporters/importers and validators for EmotionML. 
fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.processors.jaxb Contains the importer and exporter for the Info elements using JAXB. 
fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.processors.json Contains the importer and exporter for the JSON format. 
 

Uses of EmotionMLProcessor in fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.processors
 

Subclasses of EmotionMLProcessor in fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.processors
 class EmotionMLExporter
          A EmotionMLExporter is an EmotionMLProcessor that exports EmotionML objects in an OutputStream by first building DOM elements corresponding to them then validating them.
 class EmotionMLImporter
          A EmotionMLImporter imports EmotionML elements from the InputStream by first reading the stream as a DOM Element, then by validating the DOM Element with respect to the EmotionML standard and eventually by building EmotionML objects.
 

Uses of EmotionMLProcessor in fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.processors.jaxb
 

Subclasses of EmotionMLProcessor in fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.processors.jaxb
 class JaxbEmotionMLExporter
          A JaxbEmotionMLExporter is an EmotionMLExporter that exports Info objects using JAXB.
 class JaxbEmotionMLImporter
          A JaxbEmotionMLImporter imports <info> elements as Info object with JAXB.
 

Uses of EmotionMLProcessor in fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.processors.json
 

Subclasses of EmotionMLProcessor in fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.processors.json
 class JsonEmotionMLExporter
          A JsonEmotionMLExporter is an EmotionMLExporter whose writer is a JsonEmotionMLWriter.
 class JsonEmotionMLImporter
          A JsonEmotionMLImporter is an EmotionMLImporter whose reader is a JsonEmotionMLReader.
